A 48-HOUR SLEEPING SHOW!

1043
01:01:22,720 --> 01:01:24,180
WHO IS THAT?

1044
01:01:24,263 --> 01:01:25,848
PLEASE WAKE HIM UP

1045
01:01:25,932 --> 01:01:28,101
TEACH HIM SOME PROFESSIONAL SKILLS
AND SEND HIM TO A FACTORY!

1046
